<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1250304-is-it-possible-to-read-the-series-out-of">Is it possible to read the series out of order, or is there info from the previous books that is needed for this book?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1250304'><a id="like_count_community_question_1250304" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1250304?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F34868170-a-merciful-secret">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
