<div id="review_3567514438" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3567514438" />
    <a title="Teresa" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/7793520-teresa"><img alt="Teresa" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1573679482p2/7793520.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3567514438?book_show_action=true">Oct 01, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Teresa" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Teresa" href="/user/show/7793520-teresa">Teresa</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Audible Audio " href="/book/show/49245600-a-merciful-secret">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7793520-teresa?shelf=dark">dark</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7793520-teresa?shelf=detective">detective</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7793520-teresa?shelf=drama">drama</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7793520-teresa?shelf=crime">crime</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7793520-teresa?shelf=mystery">mystery</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7793520-teresa?shelf=suspense-thriller">suspense-thriller</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3567514438" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16650351024489375608"><i>A Merciful Secret</i> is another excellent installment in the <i>Mercy Kilpatrick</i> series. This series is really starting to heat up for me! You never know which way it will go, and this time around, FBI agent Mercy Kilpatrick must contend with two murders, both victims slashed to death multiple times. On her way home from her cabin in the woods late at night, she encounters a bloodied young girl whose grandmother, Olivia, is one of the victims. Upon further investigation, it seems the girl’s mother, Sa</span>
  <span id="freeText16650351024489375608" style="display:none"><i>A Merciful Secret</i> is another excellent installment in the <i>Mercy Kilpatrick</i> series. This series is really starting to heat up for me! You never know which way it will go, and this time around, FBI agent Mercy Kilpatrick must contend with two murders, both victims slashed to death multiple times. On her way home from her cabin in the woods late at night, she encounters a bloodied young girl whose grandmother, Olivia, is one of the victims. Upon further investigation, it seems the girl’s mother, Salome, and grandmother are both witches. Huh?<br /><br />I enjoyed the plot and the suspense in this book and the ongoing relationship with Sheriff Truman Daly. It seems Truman has a bit of a connection to Salome, the Momma witch. Even though this case belongs to the neighboring county sheriff’s department, Mercy and Truman plunge in to investigate the perplexing murders and soon find themselves immersed in something other-worldly. It all ended in an unbelievable finale that had me on the edge of my seat. I am excitedly looking forward to the next book. I listened to this via Audible, and the narrator, as usual, did a wonderful job. Four freaky stars!</span>
  <a data-text-id="16650351024489375608" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

<tr class="no_border feedFooterReview" id="update_comment_stuff_Review3567514438">
