<div id="review_2230263100" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2230263100" />
    <a title="Debby*BabyDee" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/56322436-debby-babydee"><img alt="Debby*BabyDee" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1643391183p2/56322436.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2230263100?book_show_action=true">Feb 06, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Debby*BabyDee" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Debby*BabyDee" href="/user/show/56322436-debby-babydee">Debby*BabyDee</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/56322436-debby-babydee?shelf=a-series-reads">a-series-reads</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/56322436-debby-babydee?shelf=x-2019-book-challenge">x-2019-book-challenge</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/56322436-debby-babydee?shelf=authors-e-f">authors-e-f</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/56322436-debby-babydee?shelf=a-audible-ku-google">a-audible-ku-google</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2230263100" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9237613985927887488">Total fan of Kendra Elliot and finishing up this series is going to be great. This was a really, really good mystery thriller with a bit of romance mixed in. It has its share of secrets, twists and turns and as mentioned quite a bit of mystery that keeps you listening/turning the page to the end.<br/><br/>Mercy is flagged down in the middle of the night by a young girl to a mountain cabin where her grandmother lay dying. The woman eventually dies and Mercy is determined to bring the woman&apos;s killer to just</span>
  <span id="freeText9237613985927887488" style="display:none">Total fan of Kendra Elliot and finishing up this series is going to be great. This was a really, really good mystery thriller with a bit of romance mixed in. It has its share of secrets, twists and turns and as mentioned quite a bit of mystery that keeps you listening/turning the page to the end.<br /><br />Mercy is flagged down in the middle of the night by a young girl to a mountain cabin where her grandmother lay dying. The woman eventually dies and Mercy is determined to bring the woman's killer to justice. Unfortunately, a judge the day before was also killed similar to the woman in the mountain cabin. FBI Special Agent Ava McLane (Callahan and McLane Series) gets involved in the investigation along with Truman. Ava, Mercy and Truman must work together to uncover the killer before he strikes again.<br /><br />This is a story where secrets can never stay hidden...for this case and for Mercy. This is another good one from Elliot that always keeps you guessing. The narration was very good by Ms. Schnaubelt. Loving the series and highly recommend.<br /><br />5-Stars</span>
  <a data-text-id="9237613985927887488" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


